<div data-role="collapsible">
	<h1>(Mathematical Reasoning and Aptitude by Dhrub Singh Sir)</h1>

<div data-role="collapsible">
	<h1>(Quantitative Aptitude by Bharat Gupta Sir)</h1>
<p class="video">
	<span class="video_name">(Quantitative Aptitude by Bharat Gupta Sir) Lecture-02 || Simplification (Part-01)</span>
	<a href="https://kgs.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/pdfs/57e89bff-6582-46eb-b57c-7df3f671cc7f.pdf" target="_blank"><h5>Download PDF</h5></a>
